# 📊 Sales Data Analysis & Dashboard Project

## 🔍 Overview
This project analyzes sales data to uncover key business insights and presents them through a clean and interactive dashboard using Excel. It includes data cleaning, analysis with pivot tables, and visualization for decision-making support.

---

## 🧩 Dataset
- **Source:** [Kaggle - Superstore Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vivek468/superstore-dataset-final)
- **Format:** CSV
- **Fields:** Order Date, Ship Mode, Segment, Country, City, State, Region, Category, Sub-Category, Sales, Quantity, Discount, Profit

---

## 🛠 Tools Used
- **Microsoft Excel** – Data cleaning, pivot tables, charts, dashboard
- *(Optional in future)*:
  - **Power BI / Tableau** – Interactive dashboards
  - **Python (Pandas/Matplotlib)** – Advanced analysis

---

## 🧾 Objectives
- Clean and prepare sales data
- Perform exploratory data analysis (EDA)
- Identify key metrics (total sales, profit, top products, regional performance)
- Create visual dashboards with slicers and charts
- Summarize insights for business decision-making

---

## 🧪 Steps Performed

### 1. Data Import & Understanding
- Loaded the dataset in Excel
- Reviewed column types, checked for inconsistencies

### 2. Data Cleaning
- Fixed date formatting
- Removed blank rows and duplicates
- Handled missing values if any

### 3. Data Analysis (EDA)
- Created Pivot Tables for:
  - Sales by Region
  - Sales by Month
  - Profit by Category/Sub-Category
  - Top 10 selling products

### 4. Visualization
- Charts Created:
  - Line chart for monthly sales trends
  - Bar chart for top products
  - Pie chart for category sales
  - Heatmap for Region vs Category

### 5. Dashboard Creation
- Combined charts and slicers in a clean layout
- Made data filterable by Region, Category, and Date

### 6. Business Insights
- Found most/least profitable regions and products
- Identified high-discount, low-profit segments
- Suggested business actions for growth

---

## 📈 Sample Insights
- 📌 West Region contributed highest profit
- 📉 Furniture category had high sales but low profit
- 🛍️ “Binders” was one of the top-selling sub-categories
- ⚠️ High discounts in the “Tables” category led to loss

---

